# Inspect Elements 

This project is an open-source front-end application that helps users scan food labels and identify different additives. The application uses a database of food additives to provide information about each additive, including its name, purpose, and potential health impacts.

## Features to be implemented 

* 🔬 Scan food labels and identify different additives
* 📖 Get information about each additive, including its name, purpose, and potential health impacts
* 🌎 Share your findings with others

## How to use

1.  📸 Open the application and take a photo of the food label
2. 🔎 The application will scan the label and identify the different additives.
3. 🖱️ Click on an additive to get more information about it.
4. 🌎 Maybe you can share your findings with others.
